locality: Réserve Naturelle Intégrale de Marojejy, 10.5 km NW of Manantenina,near source of Andranomifototra River, NE of summit of Marojejy.Near Camp 4 (where GPS reading was taken) and forested slopesnorth of the camp. Forest with trees up to 20 m tall along riversand sheltered valleys, stunted to 10 m tall on steeper slopes andalong gentle ridges. With Guy Rafamantanantsoa.
Fort-Dauphin, Eminiminy, RNI #11 Andohahela, parcelle #1. Campement 4, sur la crête.
